WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.317 --> 00:00:01.269
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.269 --> 00:00:06.608
I'm excited to be with you again today; I think this is the third video in a row.

00:00:07.410 --> 00:00:09.660
This video is pretty serious.

00:00:09.924 --> 00:00:15.120
The Lord has put on my heart—I'm going to tell you the things I've been praying about.

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:22.037
I've been praying over Italy and all the little tremors and the volcano.

00:00:24.708 --> 00:00:26.136
I'm going to tell you what I saw.

00:00:26.136 --> 00:00:27.579
I was caught up in the Spirit.

00:00:27.579 --> 00:00:33.450
I was just praying in the Spirit, I was worshiping, and all of a sudden I was shot up.

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:42.079
I was looking over Italy, and Italy was so small.

00:00:43.113 --> 00:00:50.379
I was so high—I guess that's the way I want to say it—I was really, really high and I was looking down.

00:00:50.712 --> 00:00:55.847
All of a sudden, I could see a black blanket over the water over Italy.

00:00:58.754 --> 00:01:05.130
It looked like a thick cloud, but it was as black as molasses—very, very dark.

00:01:05.130 --> 00:01:16.349
It was all over the water and there were black clouds going through all the houses.

00:01:28.290 --> 00:01:35.834
It looked like a smog all around the houses.

00:01:36.852 --> 00:01:46.906
I could see the rooftops of the homes because I was up, and I could see the lights on in the houses.

00:01:46.906 --> 00:01:51.639
Angels were descending into Italy.

00:01:51.639 --> 00:02:03.754
Above, the Lord pointed my attention to a massive circle, a humongous portal that was over the country of Italy.

00:02:17.835 --> 00:02:18.173
It was over where the earthquake happened last night, where I told you the volcano is at by Pompeii.

00:02:26.910 --> 00:02:29.180
There was this massive portal and there were angels in it.

00:02:29.180 --> 00:02:36.840
The angels were coming out of this massive portal, and the portal was like it was breathing—it was alive.

00:02:46.140 --> 00:02:50.955
It was swirling, and there were clouds all in it.

00:03:02.657 --> 00:03:02.991
It looked like it was opening up, and all of a sudden these angels started coming out of this massive portal—thousands of them.

00:03:03.660 --> 00:03:06.659
They were all coming down like a staircase.

00:03:14.477 --> 00:03:17.234
It was like they were all descending, but they were lined up like soldiers coming out of this massive portal over Italy.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:26.286
It looked like they were coming downstairs, but I could not see stairs.

00:03:26.286 --> 00:03:33.822
Through the portal, there were clouds coming out as the portal was breathing and turning.

00:03:35.504 --> 00:03:36.885
It was swirling; it was alive.

00:03:43.740 --> 00:03:44.160
The clouds coming out of the portal were humongous and beautiful—pink, blue, and purple.

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:46.500
I believe it was Heaven.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:53.605
These angels were all coming down and descending onto the Earth.

00:03:58.219 --> 00:04:07.406
When they got to a certain place in the atmosphere between the portal and the Earth, they started to spread out like ants all over the place.

00:04:10.559 --> 00:04:11.160
They started scattering and they were coming even faster down onto those homes.

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:18.360
All of a sudden, each angel was going to a place; they were on a mission, moving at the speed of light.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:22.671
They were moving down, and they all had beautiful robes and gowns on.

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:32.620
It was the most amazing thing.

00:04:38.889 --> 00:04:42.233
The whole time, I'm sitting here in this chair praying in the Spirit and seeing all this, soaking it all in.

00:04:46.739 --> 00:04:50.719
I'm trying so hard to explain everything the Lord showed me in detail: the black smog.

00:04:50.719 --> 00:04:53.159
I was asking the Lord what all that black smog was.

00:04:59.733 --> 00:05:03.497
He showed me that from coast to coast, there's a lot of sex trafficking in Italy.

00:05:04.050 --> 00:05:11.869
I don't know if people don't know about it, but he was showing that there was a lot of corruption and trafficking in Italy.

00:05:12.682 --> 00:05:18.009
There was sand and things he was showing me about this.

00:05:20.460 --> 00:05:33.270
Those angels were coming down, going to these homes, and they were making a motion with their hand, like 'Come on,' telling the people to leave.

00:05:40.007 --> 00:05:40.293
It was a warning.

00:05:43.671 --> 00:05:44.356
Every angel was waving the people to come on.

00:05:46.980 --> 00:05:47.280
They did this for several minutes.

00:05:57.549 --> 00:06:02.888
In the Spirit, you couldn't really tell a time frame, but you could sense an urgency on their faces.

00:06:05.048 --> 00:06:11.265
It felt like such an urgency of a warning, telling the people to leave.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:18.830
They didn't say anything; I could just see by their body language that they were in a hurry.

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:30.240
All of a sudden, all of the angels stopped their arms, and I knew people were praying.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:39.917
I could feel the intercessory prayers from the saints, from the Christians, from people interceding for Italy in the Spirit, praying in tongues.

00:06:41.420 --> 00:06:46.200
You could feel the blanket of prayer coming out of that portal.

00:06:56.039 --> 00:07:00.094
You could feel the intercessory prayer going on.

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:15.420
All of a sudden, all the angels froze and turned their bodies to look back up to the massive swirling light, the portal.

00:07:17.813 --> 00:07:22.139
All of a sudden, they started shooting back up into that portal, and then it was over.

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:41.742
Then the Lord took me to another part of the vision.

00:07:42.768 --> 00:07:47.819
He said, 'I want you to focus on the canary.

00:07:47.819 --> 00:07:53.580
A canary Braden, what is the meaning of a canary in a coal mine?

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:55.139
Study this out.

00:07:55.139 --> 00:08:00.519
' I saw a yellow canary in a cave, and there were gases.

00:08:00.519 --> 00:08:07.460
I could see a gas coming up out of the ground like a smog.

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:17.080
The canary was swinging in a cage.

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:20.340
I saw this birdcage in the spirit realm.

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:26.363
I saw the canary on the little swing, swinging back and forth and chirping.

00:08:31.702 --> 00:08:31.919
All of a sudden, I looked down because I could see this mist-like gas coming up out of the ground.

00:08:32.959 --> 00:08:45.105
I took my eyes off the canary, and when I looked back, the canary was dead in the bottom of the cage—lifeless and completely gone.

00:08:56.138 --> 00:08:56.415
It happened so quickly; the gases came up and took the canary out.

00:09:09.366 --> 00:09:17.780
This is part of the vision the Lord showed me about the angels and this gas coming up out of the ground in Italy.

00:09:17.780 --> 00:09:23.640
I don't know what that was—if it was from the volcano or whatever.

00:09:26.940 --> 00:09:31.620
But I told you all I saw hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:09:31.620 --> 00:09:33.580
I saw a massive wave coming.

00:09:34.233 --> 00:09:37.028
The Lord said, 'Pay attention to the water.

00:09:37.028 --> 00:09:40.959
' I saw the earthquakes in the water, and the people weren't paying attention.

00:09:41.209 --> 00:09:49.820
The water was what the Lord kept putting my attention to in the past visions—look at the water in the coves.

00:09:51.323 --> 00:09:53.055
He kept pointing me to that in the spirit realm.

00:09:54.087 --> 00:10:00.143
I could see with my spirit eyes what the Lord was showing me: the water in the gulf area right there by Pompeii.

00:10:00.930 --> 00:10:05.459
This is just what the Lord is showing me.

00:10:07.859 --> 00:10:08.139
I know, like I said, a major 4.

00:10:08.139 --> 00:10:12.993
4, I believe, happened last night.

00:10:13.267 --> 00:10:17.427
I saw all the rocks and the devastation, the people, and the sirens going off.

00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:33.309
There was a video my wife gave me from someone on Facebook; they were putting it on their feed there, and she was showing me, saying, 'Listen to this.

00:10:33.309 --> 00:10:39.427
' So I looked at it and I was like, 'Oh my goodness.

00:10:39.427 --> 00:10:51.283
' I guess this just happened yesterday, last night—it was our night—so not even 12 to 24 hours ago.

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:59.400
The electric grid situation is escalating, and things are really getting intense.

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:17.960
Okay, number two: for the past week, even from last Monday—not yesterday Monday, but the week prior—three times now the Lord has spoken to me about the electric grid in America, telling me, 'Pray over the electric grid.

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:19.482
This is very serious.

00:11:19.482 --> 00:11:25.013
' I saw a cyberattack or it was a false flag attack.

00:11:25.013 --> 00:11:46.620
Like I said, I'm not going to just flat out say it was Russia or whoever; I'm telling you I saw something go on with our electric grid, and all of a sudden power went out in New York and major cities.

00:11:58.062 --> 00:11:58.397
It was completely dark everywhere because of what happened on this electric grid issue.

00:12:05.760 --> 00:12:05.980
And so He said, 'You're not taking this serious enough.

00:12:05.980 --> 00:12:14.606
' He warned me, saying, 'You need to pray about this more intently because of what is being planned and plotted.

00:12:14.606 --> 00:12:25.155
' I saw when the electric grid went down, for some people, it had the opportunity to be down for over three weeks.

00:12:34.380 --> 00:12:34.620
I saw the number three—for over three weeks.

00:12:34.620 --> 00:12:41.957
I saw a calendar, and I could see the days go by with people being without power.

00:12:48.582 --> 00:12:54.326
The Lord was warning me about these major cities and about this plot against America and about the power grid.

00:12:54.326 --> 00:12:58.989
Now, I don't know a timeframe or anything else about that.

00:12:59.914 --> 00:13:01.968
All I know is I'm interceding for this.

00:13:01.968 --> 00:13:09.446
This is on top of the Italy thing that He brought to my attention, warning me about it.

00:13:09.446 --> 00:13:33.797
Like I tried to tell you all about what He showed me a year ago about investing into a generator that had three fuel types—propane, gas, and natural gas—and having electricity for what was coming in the future, powering your home, finding ways to power your home through solar.

00:13:45.266 --> 00:13:45.699
They sell lights on Amazon, there's candles, there's all kinds of stuff for people to have light.

00:13:45.699 --> 00:14:07.714
I don't want to ever preach fear; I don't want to be a Debbie Downer and come on here and go wacko all the time, but I get these things from the Spirit of God, these warnings, and they're very intense.

00:14:07.714 --> 00:14:09.940
He warns me about things.

00:14:09.940 --> 00:14:20.733
For instance, I was praying over an ice storm one time, and He was telling me about Texas being without power.

00:14:20.733 --> 00:14:27.299
I kept seeing 'without power,' I kept seeing 'no heat,' I kept seeing a poisoning of the water—something was wrong with the water.

00:14:27.299 --> 00:14:43.400
I believe it was about three years now that they had a major cold front; a major arctic front came down out of the Arctic and through Canada, and really made everything really cold in Texas.

00:14:43.400 --> 00:14:57.015
They could not handle the electric load for all of the people trying to heat their homes, so the electric grid shut down because the windmills froze.

00:14:58.500 --> 00:15:04.289
All of the pipes in the houses burst because people were trying to drip their faucets, and so it shut down all of the water.

00:15:04.289 --> 00:15:09.408
They put out a warning not to drink the water because it had E.

00:15:09.408 --> 00:15:15.580
coli and all kinds of stuff, and you had to boil it before you could drink it.

00:15:16.593 --> 00:15:29.857
This lasted for quite a while, but before that happened, the Lord warned me to warn friends that lived in Texas and told them, 'You need to get at least 12 cases of water.

00:15:29.857 --> 00:15:45.779
' So I took it on myself, not knowing where it would affect me, so I went out and bought all the water too because of what I was seeing in the spirit; it was very alarming.

00:15:45.779 --> 00:15:52.953
It had nothing to do with my household; we had a lot of water to drink for a while.

00:15:52.953 --> 00:15:59.513
When you're seeing in the spirit, I always want to tell you: this does not always affect everybody.

00:15:59.513 --> 00:16:08.140
There's a lot of ground to cover from Canada to Mexico, from the Atlantic to the Pacific.

00:16:08.140 --> 00:16:19.290
Whenever I'm seeing in the spirit, I don't want to always alarm everybody and say the power's going out for all of America, because I don't believe that.

00:16:22.868 --> 00:16:23.160
I want you to be praying about this for your own household.

00:16:23.160 --> 00:16:33.495
It could be New York; like I said, I saw New York, I saw a major city, and I believe it was New York, but I don't want to assume.

00:16:33.495 --> 00:16:37.667
It could be Chicago, but I saw a lot of big buildings.

00:16:39.771 --> 00:16:42.446
So I want to warn you all to pray about the power grid with me.

00:16:51.832 --> 00:16:52.095
This is serious.

00:16:52.095 --> 00:17:03.215
Instead of going, 'Well, I'm just going to go out and buy everything off of Amazon from coast to coast,' because the power grid's not going to go down for the whole country for three weeks.

00:17:03.671 --> 00:17:04.709
I don't believe that.

00:17:17.051 --> 00:17:17.375
I believe that certain areas, just like my story about Dallas and what the Lord was showing me there.

00:17:17.699 --> 00:17:29.197
I thought, because I live in Oklahoma, that this was going to be about Oklahoma, all the power going out and the water going bad, and I'm trying to warn everybody.

00:17:29.197 --> 00:17:33.231
But I'm seeing in part, I'm hearing in part.

00:17:33.231 --> 00:17:39.090
When you're doing that, I always try to be quick to obey whenever He tells me something.

00:17:49.980 --> 00:17:50.153
This was a word for Texas, and it affected a lot of people in Texas—hundreds of thousands of people—and they were without power for two weeks or more.

00:17:50.153 --> 00:17:51.015
It was bad.

00:17:51.015 --> 00:18:04.362
No heat, and people were staying in sleeping bags and trying to keep warm with their families, and pipes were bursting everywhere; it was a mess.

00:18:04.362 --> 00:18:08.600
Like I said, I get these cues.

00:18:08.600 --> 00:18:16.174
Those are the three things: about Campi Flegrei in Italy and the electric grid.

00:18:27.427 --> 00:18:28.707
I hope this video blessed you.

00:18:28.707 --> 00:18:37.920
I try to give you things the Lord has given me in prayer and keep you all updated.

00:18:37.920 --> 00:18:38.820
Let's pray.

00:18:38.820 --> 00:18:47.333
I believe we can intercede right now for the people of Italy and for the people of America.

00:18:56.408 --> 00:18:56.685
Father, I thank You.

00:18:56.685 --> 00:19:01.431
Lord, right now in the name of Jesus, we lift up Italy.

00:19:09.828 --> 00:19:10.086
We lift up this volcano and the earthquakes taking place.

00:19:10.086 --> 00:19:13.313
You said, Lord, that perilous times would come.

00:19:13.313 --> 00:19:34.650
You warned us that there would be earthquakes in diverse places, there would be volcanoes and events that were fearful, that You said men's hearts would fail them for fear for looking after the things that were coming upon the earth.

00:19:43.120 --> 00:19:44.507
Father, I thank You that we are all awake and listening to what the Spirit of the Lord is saying.

00:19:44.507 --> 00:19:51.817
That we would hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice we would not follow.

00:19:51.817 --> 00:20:00.667
If we are in harm's way, if we are not listening to what the Spirit of the Lord said, shake us inside.

00:20:00.667 --> 00:20:25.728
Show us, Lord, what we're supposed to do for our families, that we'd hear You before danger comes, that we would know Your voice, Father, and that we would know the difference between the spirit of fear trying to torment us versus the Holy Ghost trying to warn us.

00:20:25.728 --> 00:20:32.520
That we will not be led by emotion; we would be led by the Holy Ghost.

00:20:36.768 --> 00:20:45.386
I pray for every single person watching this video, that they would learn to meditate on Your word and yield themselves to the Spirit of God and be able to hear Your voice clearly.

00:20:45.386 --> 00:20:51.496
We call clarity in their ears in the name of Jesus.

00:20:51.496 --> 00:21:01.394
With spiritual ears, we call supernatural giftings to see into the spirit realm, to know Your voice and hear warnings of danger.

00:21:12.960 --> 00:21:13.170
Father, I thank You that they would hear You right now concerning their lives.

00:21:13.170 --> 00:21:20.985
Clarity in the spirit, like tuning in a radio station to a clear channel, moving the antenna.

00:21:20.985 --> 00:21:43.972
'God, I'm going to put myself at Your feet, and I will be at the spout where the glory comes out, and I am not going to be in fear about what the devil's doing, but I have authority over the devil.

00:21:43.972 --> 00:21:57.135
' And I'm going to have wisdom concerning this, and I'm not going to be moved by what I see or what I feel.

00:21:57.135 --> 00:22:10.283
I am moved by what the word of God says, and we're going to hear your voice, Father, and we're going to do exactly what you tell us to do.

00:22:18.120 --> 00:22:19.875
Father, I thank you for that.

00:22:19.875 --> 00:22:22.770
Father, I pray protection over the people over Italy.

00:22:25.425 --> 00:22:27.468
I pray protection over the believers, Father; they will be out of harm's way.

00:22:35.857 --> 00:22:36.090
Father, I thank you that those angels are coming out of that portal.

00:22:56.780 --> 00:22:56.973
I thank you, Lord, that you give a strong warning even in the midnight hour, in dreams and visions, and things like that to protect the people from what's coming.

00:22:56.973 --> 00:23:05.070
Father, I thank you, Lord, that whether it's about the electric grid over Miami, from L.

00:23:11.819 --> 00:23:12.119
A.

00:23:15.149 --> 00:23:24.213
to Phoenix to Denver to Seattle, wherever it may be—the warnings that you're giving me right now—I thank you, Father, that this will not happen.

00:23:24.213 --> 00:23:27.457
We take authority over these cyberattacks.

00:23:27.457 --> 00:23:37.898
We take authority over false flag events, and we say in the name of Jesus, you will not do this.

00:23:41.415 --> 00:23:46.097
In the name of Jesus, we plead the blood of Jesus over our power grid.

00:23:49.927 --> 00:23:59.810
We say we will have power; it will not disrupt life or cause people to lose their life because they need the electricity to survive.

00:24:06.840 --> 00:24:07.680
I thank you, Father, that there is a covering over these people.

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:20.520
I thank you, Lord, that we would hear your voice concerning these things, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:24:26.699 --> 00:24:34.259
In America, I thank you, Lord, that our people would be wise on how to handle things in our NSA and the computer people.

00:24:34.259 --> 00:24:47.804
Father, I thank you, Lord, that at Homeland Security, the people would know and they would know how to protect us—the Army, the Corps of Engineers—all the people.

00:24:47.804 --> 00:24:58.109
Father, I thank you that you give wisdom, revelation, and knowledge over these people to block attacks from foreign adversaries.

00:25:11.685 --> 00:25:11.970
And if it is a false flag or whatever, Father, we ask you, God, to expose all wicked plots and plans.

00:25:11.970 --> 00:25:19.965
Expose all wicked plans in Jesus' name—uncovering, and uncovering, and uncovering in Jesus' name.

00:25:28.080 --> 00:25:33.059
We believe we receive this right now in the name of Jesus.

00:25:33.059 --> 00:25:37.757
Now, Father, I pray over their finances.

00:25:37.757 --> 00:25:53.571
Every person who sowed and believes in their covenant for a supernatural harvest concerning their finances—I pray over their finances in the name of Jesus for a hundredfold return over what they sow.

00:26:12.438 --> 00:26:13.777
I speak to their finances right now in the name of Jesus; great blessing is on their houses, great prosperity is over their home.

00:26:13.777 --> 00:26:42.765
And God, I thank you, Lord, for jobs and better jobs, raises and bonuses, settlements, interest and income, rebates and returns, checks in the mail, gifts and surprises, finding money, bills paid off, blessing, and increase.

00:27:06.739 --> 00:27:13.839
Father, I thank you, Lord, that every need they have is met and every debt is canceled in the name of Jesus.

00:27:13.839 --> 00:27:25.267
Father, I pray over their health and their bodies in wholeness and wellness.

00:27:25.267 --> 00:27:30.428
In the name of Jesus, we take authority over sickness right now.

00:27:44.807 --> 00:27:45.940
We come against the sickness and disease; we come against manifestations of cancers, diabetes, heart disease, all kinds of dementia and Alzheimer's, and like I said, PTSD and all kinds of bondage from perversions.

00:27:45.940 --> 00:27:49.379
We command it to go now in Jesus' name.

00:27:49.379 --> 00:28:10.046
From all kinds of addictions—to alcohol, to prescription medications, from drugs to all kinds of bondage—we take authority over bondage right now in the name of Jesus.

00:28:10.046 --> 00:28:19.545
Strongholds be broken off of their lives; we call bondage and strongholds to be broken by the power of the Lord.

00:28:19.545 --> 00:28:23.179
We call the blood of Jesus over this right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We plead the blood of Jesus over this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
We thank you from the North to South, the East to West; we call angels to minister to us right now in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We thank you, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We pray over rain and an abundance of rain over our areas.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We break drought in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We take authority over drought.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
We speak to the rain; we call the rain to come from the North, the South, the East, and the West.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
We call low-pressure systems to come in right now in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We call forth low-pressure systems and the moisture to come up.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
We call rain to come; we claim rain, rain, rain in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
The former rain and the latter rain, even the spiritual rain of the Holy Ghost, rain over this nation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
We call an abundance of rain to come down right now in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We call your outpouring of the spirit, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
Bring us a great outpouring, a great outflow of a great river, a tidal wave of your presence upon this nation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
We pray over the leaders, over the people who are over this country, from Joe Biden all the way down.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
We pray for even the smallest person that's in power; we say in the name of Jesus, they would have wisdom.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Father, I thank you, Lord, they would have a fear of the Lord inside of them to make godly decisions.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
In closing, Father, I just thank you, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I thank you for your presence, for in your presence there's fullness of joy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Lord, we rest in you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
We take the care out of our prayer, for if you're begging, you're not believing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
We thank you, Lord, for where the spirit of the Lord is, there is freedom, and we will not fear.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We will not fear in Jesus' name.

